reviewText: Brilliant tour de force from a multi-talented performer.  Saw it in UK.  Too bad DVDs not avail for US

Sorry to say this was a great big let down! Love Bill on Never Mind the...... hoped for more of the same. I feel sorry for those who attended Wembley, at least I could turn it off. As you show this as a deleted by manufacturer item it is obvious that they shifted them under cover of Xmas.
Still like you Bill.
